name: Moreno 700 #1
description:
The genesis of Moreno 700 colection by milangagalactica
When the light from the sky intervenes in everyday scenarios it can transform everything. Moreno 700 is a collection that tries to show this unreality of the world we live in and how contexts make space and create a mystique. Based on a work by Marcos Cousseau, reinterpreted and taken to the extreme of delirium.
